description.narrative: This activity (Health Partnership Scheme (HPS) 2010 to 2017) is a component of Health Partnership Scheme (HPS) 2010 to 2019 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £28,998,522. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Health personnel development. , with the following implementing partners: Liverpool School of Tropical Medicine, Tropical Health and Education Trust. The start date is 09-11-2010 and the end date is 30-06-2017.
